Body:
Description: Currently when i log into my account for netwrix EPP cloud hosted, I am able to enter my email as username and my password.  then it asks for an authentication code.  I never set up MFA.  How can i access my account?  please advise.  Thank you. 
V/R
Martin Ayala

What We've Learned Updated: 06.05
The customer cannot login due to accidentally enabling MFA.

What We've Learned Updated: 16.05
The customer cannot login due to accidentally enabling MFA.

Next Steps Updated: 16.05
Change the db flag for the MFA setting.
